Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: @EricTrump: "6 weeks ago, they were laughing at Harris. They were laughing at Kamala. Then all of the sudden, the convention happens and she may as well be the modern day Margaret Thatcher. That's what the media does. I'm not surprised that she's failing…”
